{"tid":2430101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 巴西有志願者打完科興後死亡 洲政府指死者是自殺","createTime":"2021-03-02T16:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T19:43:17.000Z","uid":22556,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"15d4e033401010a29bd3003f612f3b7c63ec61a3","tid":2430101,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"巴西當局稱一名志願者出現嚴重不良反應，暫停中國疫苗臨牀試驗兩天後，周三（11月11日）宣佈重啟試驗。<br />\n<br />\n此前巴西衛生監督部門未透露不良反應的詳情，但國際媒體報道指，這名志願者「死於自殺」。進行試驗的研究所負責人說，死亡與疫苗沒有任何關係。<br />\n<br />\n巴西衛生監督局在周三的一份聲明中稱，現在有足夠信息，可以恢復疫苗試驗。「很重要的是，必須澄清暫停（試驗）並不一定意味著受調查的產品質量、安全性或有效性有問題，」聲明稱。<br />\n<br />\n這種疫苗由中國科興生物研發。科興生物周二（11月10日）回應，注意到媒體有關報道，但稱對疫苗的安全性有信心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-54901747?fbclid=IwAR0_qs-zNvU-6Ns_WmRDIr58qwgvoo2n0yHveIeWGl3hWtjJ98-HcfLfk84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-54901747%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0_qs-zNvU-6Ns_WmRDIr58qwgvoo2n0yHveIeWGl3hWtjJ98-HcfLfk84&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiumyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=34a162d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-54901747%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0_qs-zNvU-6Ns_WmRDIr58qwgvoo2n0yHveIeWGl3hWtjJ98-HcfLfk84&h=59f863ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-54901747?fbclid=IwAR0_qs-zNvU-6Ns_WmRDIr58qwgvoo2n0yHveIeWGl3hWtjJ98-HcfLfk84</a>"},{"pid":"2e300bd9c8270048b5bb20d6978b3fe8b9f7bd2f","tid":2430101,"uid":37869,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"冇講錯<br />\n打疫苗=自殺"},{"pid":"193b38866713952d2ebf3e818ef57e1d7723532b","tid":2430101,"uid":45255,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"2e300bd9c8270048b5bb20d6978b3fe8b9f7bd2f","tid":2430101,"uid":37869,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"冇講錯<br />\n打疫苗=自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T17:01:24.000Z","msg":"錯，係打科興=自殺"},{"pid":"9131a1